01:09:05,400 --> 01:09:08,160
We're going back.

1937
01:09:14,589 --> 01:09:17,800
(Shanghai, House)

1938
01:09:17,800 --> 01:09:19,400
- We're finally back.
- Let's go.

1939
01:09:24,720 --> 01:09:26,640
- Xihui is here for the first time.
- Yeah.

1940
01:09:26,640 --> 01:09:28,080
- Oh, it's your first time.
- Welcome.

1941
01:09:28,080 --> 01:09:28,920
Welcome to the house.

1942
01:09:28,920 --> 01:09:30,880
A brand-new version I've never seen.

1943
01:09:31,400 --> 01:09:33,680
- You must be very excited now.
- Yes.

1944
01:09:35,240 --> 01:09:37,280
My eyes are looking everywhere now.

1945
01:09:40,680 --> 01:09:41,640
Is anyone back yet?

1946
01:09:46,000 --> 01:09:48,440
So we three are the fastest?

1947
01:09:48,440 --> 01:09:51,280
No, I think someone
should be back earlier.

1948
01:09:51,280 --> 01:09:52,200
What's this room?

1949
01:09:52,800 --> 01:09:54,360
You can have a tour first.

1950
01:09:55,040 --> 01:09:56,200
This is your room.

1951
01:09:57,200 --> 01:09:58,520
Ling Lizheng is next to you.

1952
01:09:58,960 --> 01:09:59,800
Oh, this is Ling Lizheng's room?

1953
01:10:01,720 --> 01:10:02,688
What a coincidence.

1954
01:10:10,272 --> 01:10:11,200
Let's go down.

1955
01:10:12,680 --> 01:10:13,680
Let's cook.

1956
01:10:13,680 --> 01:10:15,000
What are you going to make?

1957
01:10:15,000 --> 01:10:17,600
I bought beef, noodles, and tomatoes.

1958
01:10:30,320 --> 01:10:31,920
Whose notebook is this? So pretty.

1959
01:10:32,840 --> 01:10:34,080
To Mr. Zhou.

1960
01:10:34,080 --> 01:10:35,000
Whose journal is that?

1961
01:10:36,000 --> 01:10:37,200
This was left on the table.

1962
01:10:37,200 --> 01:10:38,160
Who wrote it?

1963
01:10:38,320 --> 01:10:39,880
What is this?

1964
01:10:39,880 --> 01:10:40,800
What's this?

1965
01:10:44,000 --> 01:10:45,200
Are we supposed to read this?

1966
01:10:46,080 --> 01:10:48,448
No, there's also something
written for Danqi.

1967
01:10:48,448 --> 01:10:49,480
Who wrote this?

1968
01:10:49,480 --> 01:10:51,560
Wait, I think someone is leaving.

1969
01:10:52,638 --> 01:10:56,928
(Skip to the next episode
Next episode is more exciting)
